              <span id="reviewTextContainer1609221941" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7512038496545671634">Like the other Pendragon books, I read these a long time ago. I still remember them fairly well. If you are a fan of the King Arthur mythology, these are a must read. More realistic than the movie Excalibur, but more fantasy elements of the King Arthur movie with Clive Owen (2004). Extremely fantastic book series.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


