        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer992970640" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16555260941524081224">This series is getting more and more awesome. Absolutely different from the original legends or any other adaptation I&apos;ve ever read or watched, yet it contains all (or rather most of) the Arthurian elements. I wonder what the next book will be about though, I think this one has a perfect finale.</span>
  <span id="freeText16555260941524081224" style="display:none">This series is getting more and more awesome. Absolutely different from the original legends or any other adaptation I've ever read or watched, yet it contains all (or rather most of) the Arthurian elements. I wonder what the next book will be about though, I think this one has a perfect finale.</span>
